             was indicted for <rs id="t17831029-23-off126" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17831029-23-off126" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17831029-23-off126" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               that he, well knowing that one 
                     <persName id="t17831029-23-person369">
                        John
                         Hopkins
                     <interp inst="t17831029-23-person369" type="surname" value="Hopkins"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17831029-23-person369" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17831029-23-person369" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                   had lately served our Lord the King as a seaman on board the Pelican, under the command of 
                     <persName id="t17831029-23-person370">
                        Cuthbert
                         Collingwood
                     <interp inst="t17831029-23-person370" type="surname" value="Collingwood"></interp>
